This modern minimalist living room embraces clean lines, a neutral color palette, and thoughtful design elements to create a serene yet sophisticated space. The design focuses on quality over quantity, with each piece carefully selected for both form and function. Natural light is maximized through large windows, while strategic lighting creates ambiance for evening use.This modern minimalist living room embraces clean lines, a neutral color palette, and thoughtful design elements to create a serene yet sophisticated space. The design focuses on quality over quantity, with each piece carefully selected for both form and function. Natural light is maximized through large windows, while strategic lighting creates ambiance for evening use.